17:22.701 --> 17:24.134
It's not that funny.

17:24.203 --> 17:25.335
I brought wood.

17:25.404 --> 17:26.303
Where'd you get it?

17:26.372 --> 17:27.538
I looted it.

17:27.606 --> 17:29.940
Looting is legal in time of crisis.

17:30.009 --> 17:32.109
Oh, it's so nice in there.

17:32.178 --> 17:33.977
Look at that. See?

17:34.046 --> 17:35.946
Good thing I bought all those Swiffers.

17:37.950 --> 17:39.249
What happened to your hand?

17:39.318 --> 17:41.118
Ah, whittling accident.

17:41.187 --> 17:42.319
Happens.

17:42.388 --> 17:45.088
We bandaged it with
tree sap and a maxi-pad,

17:45.157 --> 17:46.223
the nighttime kind.

17:46.292 --> 17:47.624
That is amazing.

17:49.228 --> 17:51.261
You know, you don't have to be here.

17:51.330 --> 17:53.430
No. I do.

17:53.499 --> 17:57.367
We got married to be together
and to do stuff.

17:57.436 --> 18:00.838
And there's good stuff and
there's crappy stuff, like this.

18:00.906 --> 18:02.172
But we're partners.

18:02.241 --> 18:03.440
And you can't do what's best for you

18:03.509 --> 18:05.809
and screw over your partner.

18:05.878 --> 18:08.011
The fact that Viv is the one
that made me realize that

18:08.080 --> 18:10.347
is really freaking me out.

18:10.416 --> 18:14.251
So, do you accept my apology?

18:15.521 --> 18:18.155
No.

18:18.224 --> 18:20.757
What do you mean, "No"?

18:20.826 --> 18:22.726
You have to earn your keep around here.

18:22.795 --> 18:25.629
Okay. Great. Perfect. What can I do?

18:25.698 --> 18:27.364
We still need the snow latrine.

18:27.433 --> 18:30.267
Yes.

18:30.336 --> 18:31.535
Yes, we do.

18:31.604 --> 18:33.383
I'm on it. How deep?

18:33.506 --> 18:36.673
If you have to ask, "How deep?"
you haven't gone deep enough.

19:01.166 --> 19:02.766
Where's my money?

19:02.835 --> 19:05.102
- Right here.
- What is this?

19:05.170 --> 19:07.237
This is all my savings.
I want you to have it.

19:07.306 --> 19:08.605
So you can go back to Guatemala.

19:08.674 --> 19:10.240
- El Salvador.
- El Salvador.

19:12.578 --> 19:14.111
Why are you doing this for me?

19:14.179 --> 19:15.846
We're partners.

19:15.915 --> 19:18.949
You don't screw over your partner.

19:19.018 --> 19:21.451
You stupid Westport boy.

19:29.562 --> 19:30.861
I'll miss you, Luz.

19:30.930 --> 19:33.730
I wish I could say the same.

19:33.799 --> 19:36.500
I'm also gonna miss that.

19:36.569 --> 19:39.703
Look who helped me dig
a toilet in the cold, hard earth

19:39.772 --> 19:41.438
with a plastic dustpan.

19:41.507 --> 19:43.974
And I brought the fish back.

19:45.377 --> 19:46.410
Oh, power's on.

19:50.182 --> 19:52.215
Mind if I join you guys?

19:52.284 --> 19:54.017
Whatever happened to this
not being your thing?

19:54.086 --> 19:56.887
I'm really sorry.

19:56.956 --> 19:59.690
I was being selfish,
and whatever Mom said

19:59.758 --> 20:02.426
when she screwed up,
can I just piggyback on that?

20:02.494 --> 20:03.860
Smart.

20:03.929 --> 20:05.195
That was good stuff.

20:05.264 --> 20:06.797
Taco in a bag?

20:06.865 --> 20:08.131
What? No.

20:08.200 --> 20:09.099
Ew.

20:13.119 --> 20:14.923
Sorry I made you dig a fake latrine.

20:15.002 --> 20:17.423
Sorry I actually used it
and the neighbors saw me.

20:22.330 --> 20:24.463
- Oh, Viv sent you a text.
- Oh, what does it say?

20:24.532 --> 20:26.399
It's a picture.

20:30.271 --> 20:32.371
Why would she send you that?

20:35.109 --> 20:36.676
She wasn't lying.

20:36.744 --> 20:39.011
Smooth as a seal.

20:39.080 --> 20:40.980
Okay.

